OL,7,FWhen Amy Howarth hears some mothers
OL,8,Fgrumbling about how little maternity
OL,9,Fleave they have with their new baby
OL,10,Fbefore returning to work, she has to
OL,11,Fbite her tongue.
OL,13,FAfter having her second daughter Coco,
OL,14,Fwho has now turned one, Amy was back at
OL,15,Fher desk working when her baby was only
OL,16,Ffive days old. She felt exhausted and
OL,17,Fwas desperate to spend time with her
OL,18,Fnew daughter.
OL,3,C'I felt forced to go back to work five
OL,4,Cdays after giving birth ` I was
OL,5,Cbleeding at my desk'
